<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="84" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="18.[136,1452,540,668]" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">
Distribution. 
<collectingCountry box="[332,400,540,564]" name="China" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">China</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion box="[410,499,540,564]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[509,599,540,564]" country="China" name="Qinghai" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Qinghai</collectingRegion>
. Remarks. The 
<typeStatus box="[349,442,575,599]" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<typeStatus box="[497,599,575,599]" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">paratypes</typeStatus>
of this species are from Qinghai-Xizang Plateau (all from 
<collectingRegion box="[1241,1327,575,599]" country="China" name="Qinghai" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Qinghai</collectingRegion>
except 
<specimenCount pageId="18" pageNumber="84" type="generic" typeStatus="paratype">one paratype</specimenCount>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[292,380,610,634]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Kaszab" box="[401,551,610,634]" pageId="18" pageNumber="84" pagination="289 - 298" refId="ref18599" refString="Kaszab, Z. 1962. Uber das System der asiatischen Lytta-Arten, nebst Beschreibung drei neuer Arten (Coleoptera, Meloidae). Annales Historico-Naturales Musei Nationalis Hungarici, 54: 289 - 298." type="journal article" year="1962">Kaszab, 1962</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Wang" box="[568,767,610,634]" pageId="18" pageNumber="84" pagination="45 - 50" refId="ref20903" refString="Wang, X. P., Wang, H. L., Ren, G. D. 2014. Notes on the genus Lytta (Coleoptera: Meloidae) from China. Entomotaxonomia, 36 (1): 45 - 50." type="journal article" year="2014">
Wang 
<emphasis box="[638,684,610,634]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">et al</emphasis>
. (2014)
</bibRefCitation>
wrongly treated the Qinghai-Xizang Plateau as equal to 
<collectingRegion box="[1368,1449,610,634]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Xizang</collectingRegion>
. The species actually does not occur in 
<collectingRegion box="[548,629,644,668]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="18" pageNumber="84">Xizang</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
